This is how trading platforms log.

🧠 Interview Questions
Why use parameterized logging?

Avoids string creation when level disabled.

Why not log in controller?

Business logic lives in service.

Why not catch and log everywhere?

Double logging problem. Let GlobalExceptionHandler log once.

Should we log before or after DB commit?

Depends:

Before → intent

After → success confirmation

Best practice → log both start and completion.

