    SUCCESS,
    FAILED
}


Then in entity:

@Enumerated(EnumType.STRING)
private AuditStatus status;


More type-safe.

💎 Production Considerations

Large systems:

Move audit logs to separate database

Or publish audit event to Kafka

Or store in data warehouse

Or archive monthly

Audit tables can reach millions of records.

